  "body": "### Description\n\nCurrently we only use the `quarkusio` repository. I can see teams wanting to have their own repository with their own jbang scripts etc.\r\n\r\nThe easiest option is to enable everything configured to jbang (as long as it respect the convention about the prefix we have set).\r\n\r\nFor more fain grained control over the enabled repositories we could use an environment variable or some short of setting. The later would possibly require a command.\n\n### Implementation ideas\n\n_No response_",
